metadata.description:
•Ása•

3500x3500 Megapixeles.

Ása is a celestial being, her job is to help living beings in the transition from life to death, it is not an easy job because she can know when a being is about to die, she must ensure that no being lives more than necessary for new beings to exist. he can feel the joys, the fears, the suffering of each being, his job is to absorb those emotions and turn them into a new life. Although that is his task, it is impossible for him not to feel the desire that things, that life does not have an expiration date, but... if things were eternal would they have the same value?
Why do humans give flowers? when they are pulled out of the ground they begin to die, could it be that the beauty of life lies in the fact that it is not eternal? where everything has an end.

If the auction of this NFT reaches a value of 0.50 ETH, the collector will be able to claim a physical painting of this work at no extra cost.
